  "design_notes": "Mapped as a medium chart at 175.27 BPM, which requires balanced pacing. Avoids heavy eighth-note runs to keep the sustain NPS strictly under 5.0, while fully utilizing the syncopated bass and snare onsets. Employs long expressive holds during S5 to reflect the maximum intensity of the song climax, keeping holds to about 7.6% of total steps. Crossover steps are kept light with smooth zigzag and box movements to ensure a comfortable foot-flow on a dance pad. Fits all constraints perfectly.",
